      <h1>Screencaststs</h1> 

      <h2>Groundhog 1: Mapping URLs to Code</h2>

      <p>In the first screencast in the Groundhog series, we use BFG
      to begin building a clone of the open source Flask
      "microframework".  At the end of the first video, we have built
      enough of Groundhog to allow users to map URLs to code as they
      might in Flask.</p>

      <a
          href="http://static.repoze.org/casts/groundhog1.flv"
          style="display:block;width:760px;height:480px;"
          id="player">
      </a>

